Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.62,0:00:14.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天下亦有　灭世之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.84,0:00:32.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mum
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.44,0:00:34.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回想起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.35,0:00:37.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那被死亡玷污的双手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.33,0:00:42.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你会梦想着能用那双手去拯救世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.80,0:00:45.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此　我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.39,0:00:51.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对　你想要去拯救世界是因为这样可以拯救你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.01,0:00:55.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛利亚　那不是Mum Death
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.37,0:00:58.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们知道现在Mum沉睡在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.31,0:01:00.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这肯定是城堡的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.11,0:01:02.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.00,0:01:04.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是真正的Mum
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.98,0:01:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是　所说的话却并非虚言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.41,0:01:13.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要被那耀眼的银色之光拯救　对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.66,0:01:21.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小切　玛利亚　先撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.56,0:01:22.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.99,0:01:26.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道　总之现在先撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.94,0:01:29.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}完完全全就是陷阱的感觉啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.61,0:01:41.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界的分解现象　正在逐渐扩大
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.29,0:01:43.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就要抵达城市区域
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.04,0:01:48.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是计划的最终阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.25,0:01:53.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么严重的伤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.22,0:01:57.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阻止卡萝尔正是我的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.50,0:02:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须要见证到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.32,0:02:09.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么炼金术士会唱歌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.31,0:02:13.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七大行星以及七律音阶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.32,0:02:16.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼金术的核心　宇宙的调和
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.70,0:02:18.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是音乐的和谐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.81,0:02:21.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由旋律编制出的绝对真理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.71,0:02:22.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.11,0:02:28.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其构成亦是同样之物的话　又有什么好奇怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.76,0:02:36.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为克服史前文明时期被施下的混乱的诅咒所引发的沟通障碍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.98,0:02:39.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类寻找了各种各样的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:46.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过知晓万象进而与世界进行调和便是炼金术
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.53,0:02:50.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而寻求通过声音与世界相连的便是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.81,0:02:51.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.96,0:02:58.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌声与炼金术　皆是为了夺回遗失的统一语言所创造的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.75,0:02:59.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:02.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然起源尚不明确
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.93,0:03:05.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你们认真想想应该也就懂了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.91,0:03:12.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是陷阱的话　应该开始奏效了才对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.37,0:03:15.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是陷阱的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.19,0:03:19.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道诱导我们的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.77,0:03:21.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威尔博士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.93,0:03:24.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如你们所见的这幅惨样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.57,0:03:29.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为失血过多不能完全掌握蒂福日城的机能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.57,0:03:29.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs42\fnA-OTF Kumoya Std R\b0\pos(1226.499,999)}Chateau de Tiffauges{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.22,0:03:30.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是费了我好大功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.85,0:03:34.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么　在战场上和我做笔交易吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.46,0:03:42.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蒂福日城的控制装置
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.46,0:03:42.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs42\fnA-OTF Kumoya Std R\b0\pos(810.501,999)}Chateau de Tiffauges{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.85,0:03:45.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能摧毁这个的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.19,0:03:48.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你脑子的CPU到底是什么年代的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.72,0:03:52.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摧毁了的话只会无法控制罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.18,0:03:53.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底要怎么做才行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.97,0:04:07.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别忘了你们在这唧唧歪歪的时候世界的分解可还在持续着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.37,0:04:15.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌声　歌声居然正在毁灭世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:20.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东京的中心正是星罗棋布的Ley Line的汇聚点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.05,0:04:22.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反向思考一下的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.59,0:04:27.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以这里为基点向全世界传播歌声自不在话下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.80,0:04:31.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为此而破坏了起保险作用的要石吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.53,0:04:33.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经束手无策了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.28,0:04:36.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不可能没有对策
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.05,0:04:40.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是山穷水尽的绝境
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.34,0:04:44.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也一定会有柳暗花明的转机…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.82,0:04:47.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛利亚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.51,0:04:57.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁我们阻挡的这机会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.02,0:04:59.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快解决Death
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.83,0:05:03.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都说了失血过多哪那么容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.30,0:05:05.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鬼头总是喜欢耍性子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.22,0:05:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然没死吗　威尔博士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.56,0:05:10.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:14.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是在更改蒂福日城的程序了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:14.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs42\fnA-OTF Kumoya Std R\b0\pos(1020.499,999)}Chateau de Tiffauges{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.82,0:05:19.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼金术的构成是分解与分析　以及…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.81,0:05:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要将机能逆转　重构分解的世界吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.05,0:05:30.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别傻了　那样的运用蒂福日城怎么可能承受得了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.05,0:05:30.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs42\fnA-OTF Kumoya Std R\b0\pos(990.501,999)}Chateau de Tiffauges{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.68,0:05:32.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候会连同你们一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.83,0:05:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对头　一起爆破
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.51,0:05:39.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎样都可以阻止分解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.35,0:05:43.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惹别人不开心真是太特么开心了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.93,0:05:49.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威尔博士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.44,0:05:56.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mum
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.83,0:06:03.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界的分解不会停止
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.48,0:06:06.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岂可为此等琐事驻足不前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.06,0:06:09.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会阻止的　用这艾尔芙娜茵的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:09.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.99,0:06:13.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,IGNITE模块的启动可能会正中卡萝尔的下怀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.52,0:06:26.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切身体会这巨大的最后一击吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.55,0:06:31.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么可能是Mum
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.81,0:06:51.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾名菲尼　乃是拥有终焉之名之人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.13,0:07:00.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对　你就是我身陷歧途执迷不悟终将成为的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.79,0:07:04.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是　黑历史去涂改掉就没事啦Death
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.91,0:07:09.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在蒂福日城爆炸之前　战胜自身过往的罪恶一起脱出吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.91,0:07:09.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs42\fnA-OTF Kumoya Std R\b0\pos(432.501,999)}Chateau de Tiffauges{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.98,0:07:32.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛利亚小姐　可以把通信器交给威尔博士吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.08,0:07:33.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:36.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要用我的方式战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.81,0:07:37.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,博士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.33,0:07:41.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将这个通信器连接到蒂福日城
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.33,0:07:41.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs42\fnA-OTF Kumoya Std R\b0\pos(1224.501,999)}Chateau de Tiffauges{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.05,0:07:43.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来协助你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.23,0:07:46.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直HIGH到爆　但是你搞得定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.08,0:07:50.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此　用Photon shpere
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.31,0:07:54.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,运用Ley Line的样板数据进行处理的话　从这里就可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.36,0:07:54.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藤尧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.39,0:07:57.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纳兹塔夏教授的遗物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.65,0:07:59.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎能任由他人肆意滥用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.01,0:08:01.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我们杀回去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,演算全部由我们来做　尽量减少你的负荷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.33,0:08:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将你已经掌控的蒂福日城的机能全部运用到重构上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.33,0:08:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs42\fnA-OTF Kumoya Std R\b0\pos(840.499,999)}Chateau de Tiffauges{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.14,0:08:28.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我犯下的罪恶　由我一个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.18,0:08:33.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,调　切歌　这里交给我　你们去帮助大家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.64,0:08:39.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战胜这份罪恶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:41.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是三人一起的话可不行Death
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.86,0:08:46.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.99,0:08:47.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,博士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.93,0:08:50.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们拼上性命也会保护你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.01,0:08:53.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,博士你一定要拯救世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.43,0:09:01.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.14,0:09:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要来妨碍吾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.60,0:09:06.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.67,0:09:14.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和翼同台共演让我非常开心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.56,0:09:20.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果还有下次的话　一定要和你唱到天亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.40,0:09:22.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛利亚　你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.16,0:09:27.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和自己拼命厮杀过的人也能和好相处的克利斯前辈太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.00,0:09:29.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直很仰慕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.90,0:09:32.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也可以的　你已经做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.66,0:09:36.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起　那一天　在不知情的情况说你伪善
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.35,0:09:39.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来很想当面给你道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.24,0:09:41.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并没有在意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.83,0:09:42.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.27,0:09:47.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了　快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.21,0:09:50.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要妨碍我和爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.82,0:09:55.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…要以我的炼金术保护世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.43,0:09:57.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阻止卡萝尔毁灭世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.91,0:10:17.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞莲娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.31,0:10:24.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手呀
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.19,0:11:09.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,检测到分解区域的修复
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.20,0:11:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是　玛利亚小姐她们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.19,0:11:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们为了迎接未来必须要付出代价吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.21,0:11:37.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蒂福日城…托付的命题…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.21,0:11:37.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs42\fnA-OTF Kumoya Std R\b0\pos(756.5,999)}Chateau de Tiffauges{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.03,0:11:42.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.35,0:11:44.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊　魂淡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.28,0:11:50.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,投降劝告
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.09,0:11:55.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你欲描绘的未来已化作尘埃凋零了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.98,0:11:57.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未来？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.31,0:12:00.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.10,0:12:02.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了　卡萝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.26,0:12:07.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的爸爸一定没有期望这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.23,0:12:16.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在烈火之中　告知我们去了解世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.76,0:12:19.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不是要我们去做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.76,0:12:21.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾当然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.66,0:12:25.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是　亡父之恨该如何消解？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.08,0:12:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾等的丧父之痛又要怎样清雪？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.40,0:12:36.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸只托付给了吾等命题　却没有告诉吾等答案啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.14,0:12:39.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.82,0:12:46.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的父亲肯定是有什么重要的事情想要告诉你们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.58,0:12:53.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在自己生命将逝时说出的肯定是最想告诉你们的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.62,0:13:01.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为炼金术士的爸爸最想告诉我们的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.77,0:13:06.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那除了真理之外不做他想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.02,0:13:16.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼金术的终点是通过知晓万象进而与世界进行调和
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.47,0:13:18.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说调和吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.15,0:13:22.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说要吾接受拒绝了爸爸的世界吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.51,0:13:25.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有说　爸爸绝对不会说这些
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.68,0:13:30.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么　我代替爸爸给你解答
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.81,0:13:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命题的答案是宽恕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.75,0:13:42.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宽恕世界的所为
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.14,0:13:45.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这正是爸爸要告诉我们的
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.10,0:13:52.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.88,0:13:59.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蒂福日城损毁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.88,0:13:59.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs42\fnA-OTF Kumoya Std R\b0\pos(899.501,999)}Chateau de Tiffauges{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:04.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完成万象默示录的未来已是镜花水月
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.55,0:14:09.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.71,0:14:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就抛却过去　蹂躏现在好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.18,0:14:23.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以呀　这样连爸爸的回忆都会燃尽的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.58,0:14:29.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道打算燃烧全部回忆炼成为战斗力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.46,0:14:33.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡萝尔　你要做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.35,0:14:35.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.66,0:14:47.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,复仇以外吾已别无选择了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.45,0:14:52.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,复仇的业火在燃尽全部回忆前都无从熄灭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.23,0:14:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔芙娜茵根本就没有期冀过复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.49,0:15:03.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯　艾尔芙娜茵所期冀的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.21,0:15:06.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,IGNITE 你认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.03,0:15:10.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,响小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.76,0:15:13.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这还真是孤注一掷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.53,0:15:17.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我并不讨厌这样　眼下绝境更是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.61,0:15:23.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这力量是艾尔芙娜茵赋予我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.91,0:15:25.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又岂会对此心怀猜疑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.02,0:15:27.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,IGNITE模块
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.86,0:15:29.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二段拔剑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.81,0:15:33.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnA-OTF Kumoya Std R}Dáin-Dáinsleif{\r}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.44,0:16:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,IGNITE模块的三阶段保险已连续解除了两个阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.94,0:16:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已从黑化阶段转入白化阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.94,0:16:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\pos(781.5,999)}nigredo
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.94,0:16:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\pos(1133.501,999)}albedo
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.73,0:16:24.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,获得强大力量同时担负的风险也在飙升
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.03,0:16:33.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠力量强压　还真是可爱如你们会做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.71,0:16:34.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.34,0:16:40.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是IGNITE的二段强化啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.86,0:16:44.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来该换吾唱了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.84,0:16:56.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力量竟然又提升…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.84,0:16:59.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这Phonic Gain究竟是何等程度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.61,0:17:02.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但等得就是这一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.89,0:17:04.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拔剑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.98,0:17:06.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全阶段保险
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.64,0:17:08.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解除
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.15,0:17:10.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnA-OTF Kumoya Std R}Dáinsleif{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.69,0:17:17.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转入最终阶段　赤化
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.69,0:17:17.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\pos(1167.499,999)}rubedo
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.46,0:17:29.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用IGNITE的力量强压过去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.22,0:17:33.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将这汹涌的Phonic Gain汇于一点全力击出
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.06,0:17:37.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,S2CA Tri-Burst
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:42.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去顶不住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.77,0:17:45.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,IGNITE的极限吾是了若指掌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.20,0:17:50.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没明白就是这样才扔给你们的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.22,0:17:59.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾之歌声可是有着凌驾于70亿人绝唱之上的Phonic Gain啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.83,0:18:06.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不足挂齿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.00,0:18:18.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是山穷水尽的绝境
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.18,0:18:22.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也一定会有柳暗花明的转机…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.55,0:18:37.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛利亚小姐…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.51,0:18:44.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威尔博士
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.17,0:18:48.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我守住了　世间的所有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.54,0:18:50.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.58,0:18:57.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救下你只是为了让世人得以知晓我的英雄英姿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.07,0:19:05.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不快去将你这羞于启齿的经历告之天下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.39,0:19:12.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说你还是像那时一样得不成器呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.35,0:19:18.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.14,0:19:20.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何这时要说爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.57,0:19:25.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Symphogear的匹配中并无奇迹立足之地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.38,0:19:29.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果想将那力量拥为己有的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.08,0:19:32.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不休不弃努力追求便是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.20,0:19:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛利亚　我成为英雄了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.52,0:19:52.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的　你就是那最差劲的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.75,0:20:09.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道还在妄想要阻止吾吗？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.03,0:20:23.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,S2CA Hexa-Convertion
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:27.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次要以Gungnir汇聚力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.94,0:20:31.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以{\fnArial Unicode MS}Airgetlámh{\r}进行控制调配
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.99,0:20:50.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后的奇迹…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.59,0:20:54.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然利用了吾放出的Phonic Gain
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.46,0:21:07.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Generator X-Drive
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.85,0:21:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.09,0:21:55.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是…奇迹的姿态…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
